janus-cloudroom conf path .................. : $sysconfdir
])    
    
echo
echo "If this configuration is ok for you, do a 'make' to start building Janus-cloudroom. A 'make install' will install janus-cloudroom plugin to the specified prefix(must be the same with Janusï¼‰. Finally, a 'make configs' will install some sample configuration files too (something you'll only want to do the first time, though)."
